      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d6c02dd4-6cd0-11e1-9174-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
