      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64, CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/bdd8c72a-6d4a-11e1-9174-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
